    <h1>How to Build Muscle After 50<br><span>(Simple Plan That Actually Works)</span></h1>
    <p class="hero-sub">Most men over 50 don't have a training problem. They have an input problem. Here's what the research actually says — and what a sustainable plan looks like.</p>
